Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:37.56,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(0,500)}He chased forever those footprints we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why must I leave the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:10.61,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Spoken in a fairly formal language]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect, I am Kanna-sama's guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot go against her wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We will have you leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we will have you live happily ever after with Kanna-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If there were many people like you in the world, our fates might be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.09,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You must not come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is already tainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tainted?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not come close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say that your name was Uraha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who broke this barrier and found a way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if I was being beckoned by something...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be gifted with a special power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a whistling arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the signal of a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,An army from somewhere is trying to invade this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That arrow was mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the power of a winged being...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pull out the arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood will only spurt out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.24,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You are such a hopeless child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you many times, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I had forgotten for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:04:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...that human flesh was this warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna, listen carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the ancient prayer that was to die with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now bestow it upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, I wanted you to live as a normal girl, without being entwined in the fate of winged beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... the thing... we finally... inherit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream that stars see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream that stars see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:50.22,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Ryukyu = Taiwan or Okinawa]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A wing fitting for faraway Ryukyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A way for our souls...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is, above all, our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It is your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you continued your trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right for me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I was living in a palace in the mountains until a while back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In truth, I had never been on such a fun voyage before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all thanks to Ryuuya-dono and Uraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that your mother is tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have something you'd like to show her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I trained a lot, so that when I met you, I could show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can really, really do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I will definitely throw them well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It will go well next time, next time, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you go around?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in front of Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you go around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been training a long time just for this day, so why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you go around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You are very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried your very best, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue; I'll be watching you the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uraha-dono,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,please do not think of this mother as heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no need for a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not touch my body; just leave it here as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I have no more regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I... just wanted to feel with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could... entwine my wings with hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and fly to wherever we wanted in the summer sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To fly with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.64,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Kanna, that's enough. That's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you let go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother doesn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother said I was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't do otedama well, then Mother will become a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be able to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother... Mother is watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,By such crude arrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for doing your job as my guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only for a short time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-sama, have some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Give it to Kanna, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this all the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When the three of us huddle together, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a friendly family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who said that a true family is one that sticks together so much that it becomes hard to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That is really true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you, do you have wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When you suddenly say something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To escape from this siege, even if it means my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, I'll let Kanna escape alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to live with Kanna-sama and Ryuuya-sama forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us live in a small cottage somewhere peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I could get us food by ploughing fields or hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's near the ocean, we can fish too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ocean, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to bother, I'd like it to be near a warm sea in the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is an ocean like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that it's an incredibly large puddle, but I've never seen one with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a puddle, it's all salt water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're deceiving me again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, Kanna-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the ocean is as wide as the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.55,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: High quality, expensive food]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat as many red sea breams and abalone as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that depends on my fishing skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There are probably also summer festivals in villages near the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They have them everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, let's dance, all three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just watching is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams are not always painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you, do not move from here, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I could forget about my wings when I was with you, Ryuuya-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my final order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,happily...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a subjugation curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The monks are cursing Kanna-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.40,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Sutra = Buddhist scripture]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not stop chanting the sutras!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect this world from the winged being, you must not hold your own lives dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuu... ya... dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll die taking with me as many of those who put Kanna through that as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get in my way, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not bluffing either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Kanna-sama be glad to see you as a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna isn't here anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still hear Kanna-sama's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's faint, but I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The voice of Kanna-sama, crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe that you are the Kannabi no Mikoto's guardians.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We have come, under orders of our master, to take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who called us was the monk Chitoku, a high priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitoku had heard of and knew about most of the situation surrounding Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A person with wings once lived in this temple too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, this temple has watched over and sometimes even helped winged beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Chitoku, generation after generation of winged beings lived and inherited the dreams of stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and, since ancient times, gave many bits of wisdom to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them is considered the source of our magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Inherited dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? We do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Winged beings, because of their strength, were held captive by the powerful men of the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and used as tools of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna's mother had taken upon herself the curses of all those who were killed in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She was "tainted" because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who invaded the mountain were the Imperial Court's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that it was meant to completely eradicate the worship of winged beings and to unify the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitoku also said that Kanna was probably the last surviving winged being in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitoku-sama, I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bestow magical powers upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was decided that we could live at the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They said Uraha was a gem that appeared only once every hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The long days and months passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I will begin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:13.03,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Tamayose = calling forth spirits to oneself]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If we use the magic of tamayose, we should know what kind of dreams Kanna-sama is having.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-dono, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my order!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you open your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you if you die and leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everyone... leaving just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wrong, Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That... is what Kanna is dreaming about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that she continuously dreams this, somewhere in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The curse that the monks at the mountain placed on her is tormenting her, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also the curse that she inherited from her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It is one that weakens those who care for winged beings, eventually sending them to their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why my wound will not heal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can ward it off with my magic, but Ryuuya-sama, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When will I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you will last a year from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The curse that has taken Kanna captive will break someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens, Kanna-sama's spirit will return to earth and will probably repeat the cycle of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However, transferring the spirit of a winged being to a human is like transferring the water of an ocean to a small container.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Before it finishes pouring in, the container will break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna-sama's spirit, without time to heal, will return to the cycle of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way to save Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave behind a child, you can leave behind your will, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If that child cannot, your grandchild will. If your grandchild cannot, your great-grandchild will inherit your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, someday, you might find a way to save Kanna-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I will dedicate all of my remaining time to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Time that passes slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In the back of the stone house, there is a text on winged beings that I compiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If our child, who will be born one day, searches for Kanna's spirit, that text should definitely be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And Uraha will teach the child magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If the child is one who has her blood, he or she should be able to become a master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He or she might be able to follow the path that we could not find.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can continue my voyage, overcoming even time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A voyage to find priceless wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing more I wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing left for me to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A bird is flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can forget if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can forget about me and Kanna and just be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:20:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna-sama and you will continue to be by my side and guide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And that makes you my companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Uraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky is so high and clear, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuuya-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go, Uraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna is waiting on the other side of that sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go with you to the ends of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I was by someone's side just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Beside someone very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind is hazy, and I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it can fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Is it all right if I just leave it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, if I walk for a bit, turn around, and don't see it following me, then that will be our farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it follows me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, set, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that you've become friends with something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.98,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Sora = sky]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave it a name, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have another?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko piko pika.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikkori.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.57,0:23:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer do I have to live like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do my best anymore if I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, I'm going.
